reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 9, 2022
reviews.reviewText: This uses a 7" display and 2500mah polymer battery that takes a 5v or 2.5a charger. It has 800 * 480 resolution with a built in 8gb rom and 265mb ram that supports a 32g SD card. It has a smart voice system that allows you to change the voice to a language you understand best. This automatically generates the best route for you to go to get there fastest. It supports postcode address, coordinates and favorite and POI search and gives you 4 route options of fast, green, short or easy. It provides you with your current speed, route planning, active lane assistant and so much more. And the best part is it comes with free lifetime map update unlike some where you must pay to upgrade it every year.
